reviewText: I never owed it I sent it back

I had a copy of this one waaaay back in High School by some miracle I was able to purchase this in the mall.  Maybe I looked a bit older then I was back then. This is one of my favorites of the series.  Carrie Westscott & Shay Marks were fantasy dream ladies for many teenage boys of the 90's.  Two thumbs up & A+ for the "Locker Room" edition of the "Wet & Wild" volumes.

  What guy doesn't dream of checking out an open college girls locker room view???  Ha LoL- Total guy fantasy in one production.
There are several Playboy Exposed DVD's that where made with the same material. They are not exactly the same but are made from the same events.

This was much better than expected.  On one hand, it gives Briana Banks top billing, which leads you to anticipate great things.  On the other hand, it is a Playboy video, so you expect the nudity to be "watered down".  But, I was pleasantly suprised!  All the girls are indeed hot enough to pose for Playboy, but the level of nudity says Penthouse all the way.
